s = w1T h. Generalizing the loss function to multi-state problems is simple and can be done either by maximizing the smallest of the C ‚àí 1 eigenvalues or their sum [21].
To make the optimization more stable we regularize the within scatter matrix by adding a multiple of the identity matrix
